{
  "video_id": "_ZW-8-NCKMw",
  "title": "Your smartphone is a civil rights issue | Christopher Soghoian",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12499.0,
      "end_time": 15220.0,
      "text": "In the spring of 2016,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15460.0,
      "end_time": 19450.0,
      "text": "a legal battle between Apple and the Federal Bureau of Investigation"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19474.0,
      "end_time": 21152.0,
      "text": "captured the world&#39;s attention."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21633.0,
      "end_time": 24971.0,
      "text": "Apple has built security features into its mobile products"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24996.0,
      "end_time": 28829.0,
      "text": "which protect data on its devices from everyone but the owner."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28853.0,
      "end_time": 33498.0,
      "text": "That means that criminals, hackers and yes, even governments"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 33522.0,
      "end_time": 34842.0,
      "text": "are all locked out."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 35580.0,
      "end_time": 37779.0,
      "text": "For Apple&#39;s customers, this is a great thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 38581.0,
      "end_time": 40620.0,
      "text": "But governments are not so happy."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 41152.0,
      "end_time": 43469.0,
      "text": "You see, Apple has made a conscious decision"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 43493.0,
      "end_time": 46530.0,
      "text": "to get out of the surveillance business."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 46770.0,
      "end_time": 49288.0,
      "text": "Apple has tried to make surveillance as difficult as possible"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 49312.0,
      "end_time": 51678.0,
      "text": "for governments and any other actors."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 53676.0,
      "end_time": 56600.0,
      "text": "There are really two smartphone operating systems"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 56300.0,
      "end_time": 57658.0,
      "text": "in the global smartphone market:"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 57682.0,
      "end_time": 59396.0,
      "text": "iOS and Android."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 59749.0,
      "end_time": 62817.0,
      "text": "iOS is made by Apple. Android is made by Google."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 63446.0,
      "end_time": 66570.0,
      "text": "Apple has spent a lot of time and money"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 66594.0,
      "end_time": 69865.0,
      "text": "to make sure that its products are as secure as possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 70458.0,
      "end_time": 73892.0,
      "text": "Apple encrypts all data stored on iPhones by default,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 73916.0,
      "end_time": 77922.0,
      "text": "and text messages sent from one Apple customer to another Apple customer"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 77946.0,
      "end_time": 79648.0,
      "text": "are encrypted by default"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 79672.0,
      "end_time": 82189.0,
      "text": "without the user having to take any actions."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 82769.0,
      "end_time": 84380.0,
      "text": "What this means is that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 84404.0,
      "end_time": 88184.0,
      "text": "if the police seize an iPhone and it has a password,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 88724.0,
      "end_time": 92366.0,
      "text": "they&#39;ll have a difficult time getting any data off of it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 92390.0,
      "end_time": 93802.0,
      "text": "if they can do it at all."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 94374.0,
      "end_time": 98512.0,
      "text": "In contrast, the security of Android just really isn&#39;t as good."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 98536.0,
      "end_time": 101582.0,
      "text": "Android phones, or at least most of the Android phones"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 101606.0,
      "end_time": 103211.0,
      "text": "that have been sold to consumers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 103236.0,
      "end_time": 106910.0,
      "text": "do not encrypt data stored on the device by default,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 106115.0,
      "end_time": 111101.0,
      "text": "and the built-in text messaging app in Android does not use encryption."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 111555.0,
      "end_time": 114249.0,
      "text": "So if the police seize an Android phone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 114273.0,
      "end_time": 117630.0,
      "text": "chances are, they&#39;ll be able to get all the data they want"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 117654.0,
      "end_time": 118946.0,
      "text": "off of that device."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 119858.0,
      "end_time": 121544.0,
      "text": "Two smartphones"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 121568.0,
      "end_time": 123901.0,
      "text": "from two of the biggest companies in the world;"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 124497.0,
      "end_time": 126282.0,
      "text": "one that protects data by default,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 126948.0,
      "end_time": 128221.0,
      "text": "and one that doesn&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 128840.0,
      "end_time": 131982.0,
      "text": "Apple is a seller of luxury goods."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 132600.0,
      "end_time": 134255.0,
      "text": "It dominates the high end of the market."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 134710.0,
      "end_time": 139640.0,
      "text": "And we would expect a manufacturer of luxury goods to have products"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 139880.0,
      "end_time": 141450.0,
      "text": "that include more features."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 141567.0,
      "end_time": 143974.0,
      "text": "But not everyone can afford an iPhone."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 143998.0,
      "end_time": 146584.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s where Android really, really dominates:"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 146609.0,
      "end_time": 149360.0,
      "text": "at the middle and low end of the market,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 149384.0,
      "end_time": 152100.0,
      "text": "smartphones for the billion and a half people"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 152340.0,
      "end_time": 154904.0,
      "text": "who cannot or will not spend"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 154928.0,
      "end_time": 157389.0,
      "text": "600 dollars on a phone."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 161275.0,
      "end_time": 167105.0,
      "text": "But the dominance of Android has led to what I call"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 167129.0,
      "end_time": 169340.0,
      "text": "the \"digital security divide.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 169365.0,
      "end_time": 172350.0,
      "text": "That is, there is now increasingly a gap"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 172374.0,
      "end_time": 176499.0,
      "text": "between the privacy and security of the rich,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 176523.0,
      "end_time": 179293.0,
      "text": "who can afford devices that secure their data by default,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 180360.0,
      "end_time": 181288.0,
      "text": "and of the poor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 181851.0,
      "end_time": 186525.0,
      "text": "whose devices do very little to protect them by default."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 187667.0,
      "end_time": 190782.0,
      "text": "So, think of the average Apple customer:"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 192130.0,
      "end_time": 196875.0,
      "text": "a banker, a lawyer, a doctor, a politician."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 197387.0,
      "end_time": 202641.0,
      "text": "These individuals now increasingly have smartphones in their pockets"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 202665.0,
      "end_time": 206138.0,
      "text": "that encrypt their calls, their text messages,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 206162.0,
      "end_time": 207697.0,
      "text": "all the data on the device,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 207721.0,
      "end_time": 211729.0,
      "text": "without them doing really anything to secure their information."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 212904.0,
      "end_time": 216948.0,
      "text": "In contrast, the poor and the most vulnerable in our societies"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 216973.0,
      "end_time": 222160.0,
      "text": "are using devices that leave them completely vulnerable to surveillance."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 223650.0,
      "end_time": 225540.0,
      "text": "In the United States, where I live,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 225780.0,
      "end_time": 229270.0,
      "text": "African-Americans are more likely to be seen as suspicious"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 229510.0,
      "end_time": 230902.0,
      "text": "or more likely to be profiled,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 231640.0,
      "end_time": 235304.0,
      "text": "and are more likely to be targeted by the state with surveillance."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 236800.0,
      "end_time": 238797.0,
      "text": "But African-Americans are also disproportionately likely"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 238821.0,
      "end_time": 241917.0,
      "text": "to use Android devices that do nothing at all"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 241941.0,
      "end_time": 244110.0,
      "text": "to protect them from that surveillance."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 244974.0,
      "end_time": 246298.0,
      "text": "This is a problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 247536.0,
      "end_time": 250450.0,
      "text": "We must remember that surveillance is a tool."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 250810.0,
      "end_time": 253458.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a tool used by those in power"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 253934.0,
      "end_time": 256192.0,
      "text": "against those who have no power."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 257173.0,
      "end_time": 261923.0,
      "text": "And while I think it&#39;s absolutely great"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 261947.0,
      "end_time": 265395.0,
      "text": "that companies like Apple are making it easy for people to encrypt,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 266355.0,
      "end_time": 270170.0,
      "text": "if the only people who can protect themselves"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 270194.0,
      "end_time": 271685.0,
      "text": "from the gaze of the government"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 271709.0,
      "end_time": 273269.0,
      "text": "are the rich and powerful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 273741.0,
      "end_time": 274928.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s a problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 275549.0,
      "end_time": 279111.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s not just a privacy or a cybersecurity problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 279739.0,
      "end_time": 281282.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a civil rights problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 282806.0,
      "end_time": 285673.0,
      "text": "So the lack of default security in Android"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 285697.0,
      "end_time": 291760.0,
      "text": "is not just a problem for the poor and vulnerable users"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 291100.0,
      "end_time": 293318.0,
      "text": "who are depending on these devices."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 293342.0,
      "end_time": 295602.0,
      "text": "This is actually a problem for our democracy."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 296237.0,
      "end_time": 297705.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ll explain what I mean."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 298514.0,
      "end_time": 301389.0,
      "text": "Modern social movements rely on technology --"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 301413.0,
      "end_time": 306836.0,
      "text": "from Black Lives Matter to the Arab Spring to Occupy Wall Street."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 307238.0,
      "end_time": 311213.0,
      "text": "The organizers of these movements and the members of these movements"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 311237.0,
      "end_time": 315177.0,
      "text": "increasingly communicate and coordinate with smartphones."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 316446.0,
      "end_time": 320297.0,
      "text": "And so, naturally governments that feel threatened by these movements"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 320321.0,
      "end_time": 323977.0,
      "text": "will also target the organizers and their smartphones."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 325462.0,
      "end_time": 327536.0,
      "text": "Now, it&#39;s quite possible"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 327560.0,
      "end_time": 331624.0,
      "text": "that a future Martin Luther King or a Mandela or a Gandhi"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 331648.0,
      "end_time": 335505.0,
      "text": "will have an iPhone and be protected from government surveillance."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 336283.0,
      "end_time": 337830.0,
      "text": "But chances are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 337854.0,
      "end_time": 341568.0,
      "text": "they&#39;ll probably have a cheap, $20 Android phone in their pocket."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 342676.0,
      "end_time": 346497.0,
      "text": "And so if we do nothing to address the digital security divide,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 346521.0,
      "end_time": 350389.0,
      "text": "if we do nothing to ensure that everyone in our society"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 351167.0,
      "end_time": 353452.0,
      "text": "gets the same benefits of encryption"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 353476.0,
      "end_time": 357133.0,
      "text": "and is equally able to protect themselves from surveillance by the state,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 357157.0,
      "end_time": 361938.0,
      "text": "not only will the poor and vulnerable be exposed to surveillance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 362404.0,
      "end_time": 365344.0,
      "text": "but future civil rights movements may be crushed"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 365369.0,
      "end_time": 367789.0,
      "text": "before they ever reach their full potential."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 367813.0,
      "end_time": 368979.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 369400.0,
      "end_time": 372111.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 375940.0,
      "end_time": 377866.0,
      "text": "Helen Walters: Chris, thank you so much."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 377890.0,
      "end_time": 379762.0,
      "text": "I have a question for you."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 379786.0,
      "end_time": 381639.0,
      "text": "We saw recently in the press"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 381663.0,
      "end_time": 387167.0,
      "text": "that Mark Zuckerberg from Facebook covers over his camera"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 387191.0,
      "end_time": 390164.0,
      "text": "and does something with his headphone mic jack."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 390189.0,
      "end_time": 392734.0,
      "text": "So I wanted to ask you a personal question, which is:"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 392758.0,
      "end_time": 393909.0,
      "text": "Do you do that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 393934.0,
      "end_time": 396513.0,
      "text": "And, on behalf of everyone here, particularly myself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 396537.0,
      "end_time": 397861.0,
      "text": "Should we be doing that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 397886.0,
      "end_time": 399654.0,
      "text": "Should we be covering these things?"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 399678.0,
      "end_time": 403839.0,
      "text": "Christopher Soghoian: Putting a sticker -- actually, I like Band-Aids,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 403863.0,
      "end_time": 406128.0,
      "text": "because you can remove them and put them back on"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 406152.0,
      "end_time": 408464.0,
      "text": "whenever you want to make a call or a Skype call."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 408488.0,
      "end_time": 410190.0,
      "text": "Putting a sticker over your web cam"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 410214.0,
      "end_time": 412890.0,
      "text": "is probably the best thing you can do for your privacy"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 412914.0,
      "end_time": 414419.0,
      "text": "in terms of bang for buck."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 414444.0,
      "end_time": 418341.0,
      "text": "There really is malware, malicious software out there"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 418365.0,
      "end_time": 420222.0,
      "text": "that can take over your web cam,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 420246.0,
      "end_time": 422116.0,
      "text": "even without the light turning on."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 422140.0,
      "end_time": 425308.0,
      "text": "This is used by criminals. This is used by stalkers."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 425333.0,
      "end_time": 430271.0,
      "text": "You can buy $19.99 \"spy on your ex-girlfriend\" software online."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 430295.0,
      "end_time": 431446.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s really terrifying."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 431470.0,
      "end_time": 433994.0,
      "text": "And then, of course, it&#39;s used by governments."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 434180.0,
      "end_time": 437239.0,
      "text": "And there&#39;s obviously a sexual violence component to this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 437263.0,
      "end_time": 440964.0,
      "text": "which is that this kind of surveillance can be used most effectively"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 440988.0,
      "end_time": 447791.0,
      "text": "against women and other people who can be shamed in our society."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 448417.0,
      "end_time": 450525.0,
      "text": "Even if you think you have nothing to hide,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 450549.0,
      "end_time": 455107.0,
